        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }\n    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }\n    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 40px 20px; }\n    .api-key-box { background: #fff; border: 3px solid #667eea; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center; }\n    .api-key { font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; color: #667eea; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-all; }\n    .button { display: inline-block; background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; margin: 20px 0; }\n    .code-block { background: #1a202c; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; overflow-x: auto; }\n    .code-block pre { margin: 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; }\n    .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }\n    .warning { background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"header\">\n      <h1>üéâ Welcome to Referrer Tracker!</h1>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">Your account is ready</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"content\">\n      <h2>Hi {{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.customer_name || 'there'}}!</h2>\n      <p>Thank you for subscribing to Referrer Tracker. Your account has been activated and you're ready to start tracking your traffic sources.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"api-key-box\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #667eea;\">Your API Key</h3>\n        <div class=\"api-key\">{{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.api_key}}</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"warning\">\n        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Keep this API key secure. Do not share it publicly or commit it to public repositories.\n      </div>\n      \n      <h3>Quick Start Guide</h3>\n      <ol style=\"line-height: 2;\">\n        <li><strong>Download the script:</strong> <a href=\"https://referrertracker.com/download\">referrer-tracker.js</a></li>\n        <li><strong>Add it to your website</strong></li>\n        <li><strong>Configure your API key</strong> (see code below)</li>\n        <li><strong>Add hidden fields to your forms</strong></li>\n      </ol>\n      \n      <h3>Installation Code</h3>\n      <div class=\"code-block\">\n        <pre>&lt;!-- Add the script --&gt;\n&lt;script src=\"referrer-tracker.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- Configure your API key --&gt;\n&lt;script&gt;\n  ReferrerTracker.configure({\n    apiKey: '{{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.api_key}}'\n  });\n&lt;/script&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- Add to your forms --&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"hidden\" name=\"rt_source\" class=\"js-rt-source\"&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"hidden\" name=\"rt_medium\" class=\"js-rt-medium\"&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"hidden\" name=\"rt_campaign\" class=\"js-rt-campaign\"&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"hidden\" name=\"rt_gclid\" class=\"js-rt-gclid\"&gt;</pre>\n      </div>\n      \n      <h3>Your Plan Details</h3>\n      <ul style=\"line-height: 2;\">\n        <li><strong>Plan:</strong> {{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.plan}}</li>\n        <li><strong>Domains:</strong> Up to {{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.domains_limit}}</li>\n        <li><strong>Monthly Events:</strong> {{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.monthly_events_limit}}</li>\n        <li><strong>Features:</strong> {{$('Build API Key Record').item.json.features}}</li>\n      </ul>\n      \n      <div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;\">\n        <a href=\"https://referrertracker.com/docs\" class=\"button\">View Documentation</a>\n      </div>\n      \n      <h3>Need Help?</h3>\n      <p>We're here to help you get started:</p>\n      <ul>\n        <li>üìö <a href=\"https://docs.referrertracker.com\">Documentation</a></li>\n        <li>üí¨ <a href=\"mailto:support@referrertracker.com\">Email Support</a></li>\n        <li>üé• <a href=\"https://referrertracker.com/tutorials\">Video Tutorials</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <p><strong>Referrer Tracker</strong></p>\n      <p>You're receiving this email because you subscribed to Referrer Tracker.</p>\n      <p><a href=\"https://referrertracker.com\">referrertracker.com</a></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
